<br>
I have only done 4 adventures so far, all at &quot;normal&quot;, these were:<br>
<br>
1. Kill X mobs in Mistmoore - passed in ~50 minutes<br>
2. Assassination in Mistmoore - passed in ~45 minutes.<br>
3. Assassination in Mistmoore - passed in ~30 minutes.<br>
4. Assassination in Rujarkian Hills - failed in 90 minutes, finished in ~10 more.<br>
<br>
